    <title>tags()</title>
    <indexterm type="parameter">
        <primary>tags()</primary>
    </indexterm>
    <informaltable frame="topbot" colsep="0" rowsep="0">
        <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colnum="1" colwidth="40pt"/>
            <tbody>
                <row>
                    <entry>Type:</entry>
                    <entry>string</entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>Default:</entry>
                    <entry/>
                </row>
            </tbody>
        </tgroup>
    </informaltable>
    <para><emphasis role="bold">Description:</emphasis> Label the messages received from the source with custom tags. Tags must be unique, and enclosed between double quotes. When adding multiple tags, separate them with comma, for example <userinput>tags("dmz", "router")</userinput>. This option is available only in syslog-ng 3.1 and later.</para>
